1
00:00:12,599 --> 00:00:14,160
Officer lady

2
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:18,199
You're tonight's biggest highlight!

3
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:22,640
Welcome to my world

4
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:10,040
The signal appeared.

5
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:14,400
Thanks for the gifts, guys.

6
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,120
Lin Xue.

7
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,040
Who would've thought?

8
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:21,319
Our show just keeps getting more exciting.

9
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,400
We've even got real cops joining in.

10
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:28,359
Watch your mouth.

11
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,560
He's using a masked signal.

12
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,400
I'm filtering it out.

13
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:33,280
Speed up the trace.

14
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:37,920
The real show

15
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,920
is about to begin.

16
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,319
The location's in Lianhai District.

17
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,680
Find out which village ASAP.

18
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:51,840
How about it,

19
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,280
officer lady?

20
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:57,200
I'm not easy to catch.

21
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:57,959
Wait.

22
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,519
Play back that footage.

23
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:00,879
Okay.

24
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:02,719
Zoom in on Lin Xue's hand.

25
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,400
What does this gesture mean?

26
00:02:07,239 --> 00:02:08,000
C.

27
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,599
Caowu Village.

28
00:02:16,439 --> 00:02:16,919
Hello.

29
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:17,680
Jiang Han.

30
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,680
Get to Caowu Village immediately.

31
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,960
Got it, Captain Wang.

32
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,560
How far to Caowu Village?

33
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,599
Three kilometers.

34
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,120
Full speed. Go!

35
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,800
Roger that.

36
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:31,199
This is just our appetizer.

37
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,319
I figure

38
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,280
you'd want to know

39
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:38,680
where you stand with your boss, right?

40
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,520
What do you say?

41
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,759
I'll give you ten seconds.

42
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:48,159
Tell those cops on the other side

43
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,319
to stop attacking my site.

44
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:52,319
Otherwise,

45
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:55,919
she'll be saying goodbye to this world.

46
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,120
Ten.

47
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,400
Nine.

48
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,439
Eight.

49
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,639
Seven.

50
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,919
Six.

51
00:03:08,159 --> 00:03:08,960
Five.

52
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,240
Four.

53
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:10,960
Stop the trace.

54
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,639
Three.

55
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,240
Two.

56
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:21,800
That's more like it.

57
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:30,080
Nothing here. Nothing.

58
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,039
Come on, check over here.

59
00:03:39,439 --> 00:03:40,000
Hold on.

60
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,319
Remember this from now on.

61
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,439
When you're at a scene with him,

62
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,280
medical gloves

63
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:51,280
are a must.

64
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,759
This is Lin Xue's glove.

65
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:56,000
The suspect must be inside.

66
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,319
Shunzi.

67
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,840
You two, watch the main gate.

68
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,439
Yang, let's look around.

69
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,560
See if there's a way in.

70
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,120
Go.

71
00:04:04,479 --> 00:04:04,919
Move.

72
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:10,319
Do you want this character

73
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:13,280
carved on your belly,

74
00:04:14,599 --> 00:04:17,199
or carved on your chest?

75
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:41,720
Don't move!

76
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:42,839
Xing Mingliang!

77
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:43,959
Drop the knife!

78
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,600
Got him.

79
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,319
So what?

80
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,319
Come on!

81
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,920
Shoot me!

82
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,439
I want to know what a bullet feels like too.

83
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:09,160
Xing Mingliang!

84
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:10,560
You're assaulting an officer.

85
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,800
That's another charge, you get it?

86
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,240
You think I give a damn?

87
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,000
They're all bitches.

88
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,360
Filthy bitches!

89
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:23,360
They all deserve to die!

90
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,240
Come on!

91
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:26,639
Shoot!

92
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:28,399
Shoot me!

93
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,160
You don't have the guts, do you?

94
00:05:34,759 --> 00:05:35,639
Come on!

95
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,319
Everyone, listen up!

96
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:42,120
If the suspect resists again,

97
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,639
you are

98
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:48,120
authorized to shoot to kill.

99
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,720
Authorized to shoot to kill.

100
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,720
Xing Mingliang!

101
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,399
This is your final warning.

102
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,560
Drop the knife!

103
00:05:55,759 --> 00:05:56,800
Or I will shoot!

104
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,160
Go ahead and shoot!

105
00:05:58,439 --> 00:06:00,360
We'll just die together, no big deal!

106
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,759
Mingliang, just stop.

107
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:04,319
Don't go any further down this path.

108
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,360
Shut up!

109
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,759
This is all because of you, you bitch!

110
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,600
I'll kill this damn cop,

111
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,959
and then I'll kill you!

112
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,360
Don't move!

113
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,800
This garage is reserved for President Su's car.

114
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:23,959
He rarely drives this car.

115
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,279
The keys.

116
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,480
I don't have them.

117
00:07:51,319 --> 00:07:53,040
Hey, you can't smash it!

118
00:07:53,199 --> 00:07:54,839
I'll take responsibility. Move aside.

119
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:01,920
I'll keep it brief.

120
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,800
While I was away at the provincial meeting,

121
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,199
something major happened at the bureau.

122
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,519
A big case has broken in Fengdu.

123
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:11,000
The situation regarding Comrade Li Kaiyang,

124
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,839
I'm sure you've all heard about it.

125
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,240
Let me make my position clear.

126
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,279
Until the truth comes to light,

127
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:20,720
no one is allowed to smear his name.

128
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,079
Xing.

129
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:24,879
Go ahead and speak.

130
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:28,839
Chief Gao,

131
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:30,439
this is my failure.

132
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,000
I bear full responsibility.

133
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:38,440
With a case this significant,

134
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,799
as head of the Criminal Investigation Division,

135
00:08:41,879 --> 00:08:42,600
you should be held accountable.

136
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:46,639
But as Xing Mingliang's immediate family,

137
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,120
you must recuse yourself.

138
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:50,399
Yonglin,

139
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:52,440
from this moment on,

140
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,720
you'll lead all the comrades on the team,

141
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,600
to work around the clock.

142
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:57,000
Even without food or rest,

143
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,799
you must crack this case.

144
00:08:59,240 --> 00:08:59,720
Yes, sir.

145
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,039
Comrades,

146
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,080
I expect everyone to give 120 percent

147
00:09:05,399 --> 00:09:06,639
and win this tough battle.

148
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,919
Because this concerns not only

149
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,000
the reputation of the Fengdu police,

150
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:13,720
but also

151
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:16,000
the safety of Fengdu's citizens.

152
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,919
Thank you all for your hard work.

153
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,039
Please, sit down.

154
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,080
What are you doing?

155
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,039
What are YOU doing?

156
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,159
I'm investigating.

157
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,000
So am I.

158
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,840
Aren't you interrogating Xing Mingliang?

159
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,840
He admitted to kidnapping women and filming it.

160
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:04,840
But he flatly denies framing Captain Li.

161
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:06,919
That's exactly why we have to keep at it.

162
00:10:06,919 --> 00:10:07,840
Why are you following me?

163
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,919
Captain Li isn't just your boss.

164
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:12,720
He's also family to me at Major Crimes.

165
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,320
I want the truth even more than you do.

166
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:16,360
To clear his name.

167
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:36,679
Parking in such a remote spot,

168
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:37,720
He must be hiding something

169
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:39,120
Let's go

170
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:53,960
Chief Xing

171
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:15,840
Someone's upstairs.

172
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:16,759
Did you bring your gun?

173
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:27,879
Chief Xing is still breathing.

174
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,720
Call an ambulance, now!

175
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:45,600
Come here.

176
00:11:56,279 --> 00:11:57,399
Weren't you supposed to be dead?

177
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,440
Why are you here?

178
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,320
The killer's still around.

179
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,440
Wait, am I the one who's dead?

180
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:08,519
Why are you pinching me?

181
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:23,039
Are you out of your mind?

182
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,840
The guy's got a crossbow.

183
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:26,519
And you charge in bare-handed?

184
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:29,080
You think you're Astro Boy or something?

185
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,879
Weren't you supposed to be dead?

186
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:35,159
What the hell is going on?

187
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,600
It's a long story.

188
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:38,279
Let's catch him first.

189
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:39,519
Okay?

190
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:41,440
Go.

191
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:43,960
Move!

192
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:54,559
Let's split up.

193
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,519
You be careful.

194
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,279
Boss

195
00:13:16,799 --> 00:13:17,960
What the hell is going on?

196
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:18,879
Weren't you dead?

197
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:19,679
How are you alive again?

198
00:13:20,639 --> 00:13:22,000
And why did Chief Xing fall?

199
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,559
Say something!

200
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:26,639
You didn't actually commit a crime, did you?

201
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:27,840
We'll talk about that later.

202
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,480
How's Chief Xing?

203
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,240
Li Kaiyang.

204
00:13:31,759 --> 00:13:33,440
Why don't you ask how I'm doing?

205
00:13:34,159 --> 00:13:35,679
Do you know that ever since you died,

206
00:13:35,679 --> 00:13:36,840
how devastated the team has been?

207
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,360
Do you know that since I became an adult,

208
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,480
I've never cried.

209
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,519
But because of you...

210
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,279
I'll explain everything.

211
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:45,840
Trust me.

212
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:47,960
How am I supposed to trust you?

213
00:13:48,519 --> 00:13:49,639
You're a fugitive now.

214
00:13:49,799 --> 00:13:50,759
I'm a cop.

215
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:51,879
What am I supposed to do?

216
00:13:54,799 --> 00:13:55,600
I'll go back to the unit with you.

217
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:38,080
Comrade Li Kaiyang

218
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,320
You've been through a lot.

219
00:14:53,639 --> 00:14:54,360
Everyone, have a seat.

220
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:01,759
Kaiyang

221
00:15:02,399 --> 00:15:03,039
You sit too.

222
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:04,240
Yeah.

223
00:15:13,919 --> 00:15:14,519
Jiang Han

224
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:15,879
Sit down.

225
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,240
Kaiyang

226
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:26,799
Let's hear the answer.

227
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,600
You're quite good at posing riddles.

228
00:15:40,799 --> 00:15:42,519
And you're quite good at solving them.

229
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,200
A carp.

230
00:15:48,399 --> 00:15:49,039
What?

231
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:51,360
That mission we were on,

232
00:15:51,879 --> 00:15:53,879
I caught a carp this big too.

233
00:15:59,519 --> 00:16:00,600
Once, the two of us were on a mission,

234
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:01,799
right here.

235
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,279
You disguised yourself as a fisherman.

236
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,399
The suspect never showed up,

237
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:07,440
but you reeled in a five-pound carp.

238
00:16:08,279 --> 00:16:09,159
I remember that.

239
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,440
Back then you told me,

240
00:16:13,879 --> 00:16:14,639
"This is amazing.

241
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:17,000
I can brag about this to my grandson forever."

242
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:19,600
Lucky for me,

243
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,360
it's a granddaughter.

244
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:23,639
That mouth of yours,

245
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:26,480
is a classic case of harming others for no gain.

246
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,960
But you've got some nerve, kid.

247
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,240
With everything going on,

248
00:16:31,919 --> 00:16:32,960
you still dared to stay at a hotel?

249
00:16:33,879 --> 00:16:35,080
If I didn't leave you a clue,

250
00:16:35,519 --> 00:16:36,360
how would you find me?

251
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,279
Were you that certain

252
00:16:38,879 --> 00:16:39,799
I wouldn't arrest you?

253
00:16:40,399 --> 00:16:41,480
If you hadn't gone easy on me,

254
00:16:42,679 --> 00:16:44,759
even with wings I couldn't escape the Criminal Investigation Unit.

255
00:16:45,679 --> 00:16:47,679
Provincial Criminal Police Marksmanship Award,

256
00:16:49,080 --> 00:16:50,000
you've won it three times.

257
00:16:52,879 --> 00:16:55,320
It was just an easy favor.

258
00:16:56,159 --> 00:16:57,000
Chief Xing

259
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:59,080
bringing a gun into the interrogation room

260
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,799
meant he intended to let you go.

261
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,120
You know,

262
00:17:02,759 --> 00:17:04,079
you may seem rough around the edges,

263
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,279
but you're more meticulous than anyone.

264
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:10,519
Telling Chief Xing I wasn't cuffed was a double entendre, right?

265
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,079
Both a warning,

266
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:15,559
and a test.

267
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:16,519
Hey,

268
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:19,920
When did you start suspecting Chief Xing?

269
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,480
After Su Zhuang's death,

270
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:29,119
I secretly pulled the hospital surveillance.

271
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:31,319
The only ones who entered Su Zhuang's room alone

272
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:34,160
were you and Chief Xing.

273
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:37,400
Then why did you rule me out?

274
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:38,720
Because of Xing Mingliang.

275
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:41,240
I had a feeling that everything bad Xing Mingliang did,

276
00:17:42,079 --> 00:17:42,920
Chief Xing knew about.

277
00:17:43,279 --> 00:17:44,839
And he'd been to Xu Wenwen's club.

278
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,440
Jiang Han's father, Chief Jiang,

279
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,599
got photos of it.

280
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,920
Not bad, kid.

281
00:17:54,359 --> 00:17:55,720
You even pulled Chief Jiang into this.

282
00:17:59,359 --> 00:18:00,599
But up to now,

283
00:18:01,359 --> 00:18:03,160
our suspicions about Xu Wenwen

284
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,720
are all based on inference and guesswork.

285
00:18:06,119 --> 00:18:07,599
We have no solid evidence.

286
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:09,279
Then let's follow the chain of profit,

287
00:18:10,240 --> 00:18:10,960
and dig deep.

288
00:18:13,839 --> 00:18:14,480
Think about it.

289
00:18:14,839 --> 00:18:16,720
Xu Wenwen took such huge risks

290
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,000
